  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1179">
<l>vārākkāṟ ṟuñcā variṟṟuñcā āyiṭai </l>
<l>yāraña ruṟṟaṉa kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When he is away they do not sleep; when he is present they do not sleep; in either case, mine eyes endure unbearable agony.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
